      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DID SHE (8) failed to feature last start after missing the jump at this track, but prior to that won by half a length at this track (22.84) beating That's My Cousin in a Grade 5 on March 17. Won at her only start from this box. Has ability and can bounce back. FRED THE FOX (2) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Bendigo over 500m behind Sorella (29.26) in a Grade 5. Was a winner the start prior. Has won two of five starts from this draw. Expected to feature in the finish. COMEBACK CHARLIE (1) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 5th (23.24) at this track. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Can do much better this time. PRETTY PANAMA (6) can play a role in the finish without surprising.",
